{"tid":179802,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求有效既睡眠方法","createTime":"2017-03-30T13:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T05:03:50.000Z","uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47f0a091bd2737d6c675a369c50cc7561e25c5f1","tid":179802,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:12:31.000Z","msg":"小弟一般11點幾訓 7點起身返工 冇失眠問題 都算容易入睡 所以都有7粒鐘睡眠時間 應該係足夠 但唔知點解訓醒起身都係攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近呢幾日仲會半夜4點左右醒一醒(唔知點解真係咁岩幾日都係呢個時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有2次係隻腳抽筋醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  )醒果陣唔算攰 望一望手機個時間 仲幾開心因為仲有3粒鐘訓 心諗依刻都唔係攰 到時訓醒應該幾精神 好快就訓返着 點知7點醒果刻仲攰過半夜醒果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有冇咩方法/睡姿係令到個人訓6,7粒鐘都會好足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bcb50dc2ab62f130b62e116ca6d9e54fc6cf29","tid":179802,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同樣情況<br />\n3或者4點都會醒一次<br />\n<br />\n明明訓左七 八個鐘都係會好攰"},{"pid":"1ad0d4c9987f54d24d3a9602cd07abd24c72d58d","tid":179802,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同樣情況<br />\n3或者4點都會醒一次<br />\n<br />\n明明訓左七 八個鐘都係會好攰</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0579de20ee360e95961ef3e81718a011eadbc415","tid":179802,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfcfa3c93f8d1e306b5cf47eac94447d7883e131","tid":179802,"uid":62141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"之前我又係十二點幾訓 七點幾起身 但係成日六點無端端醒左 本身我都繼續訓 <br />\n但發現六點個精神狀態比七點個仲好<br />\n跟住爽性唔訓 係中午食完飯補個半個鐘覺就掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5164d8b8556b12ff7619d31e3b3d171f15904f1","tid":179802,"uid":93430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:04:14.000Z","msg":"試下提早半個鐘訓<br />\n訓之前唔好係熄晒燈既環境下咁手機/做d要好用腦既野"},{"pid":"e98ec3a02e378ff040fa2481baf24e83e02cc594","tid":179802,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:07:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前我又係十二點幾訓 七點幾起身 但係成日六點無端端醒左 本身我都繼續訓 <br />\n但發現六點個精神狀態比七點個仲好<br />\n跟住爽性唔訓 係中午食完飯補個半個鐘覺就掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想午睡 但我份工係冇機會訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31135edd5264d1671087e484ff4c5280ba659b9","tid":179802,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下提早半個鐘訓<br />\n訓之前唔好係熄晒燈既環境下咁手機/做d要好用腦既野</blockquote><br />\n提早半個鐘真係有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上左床我好少玩手機 特別係呢排 一心都係想訓 冇咩野諗亦唔敢諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而我又真係好快訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84323bf0aae992cd39b273d2b52680d1cc313117","tid":179802,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T15:02:25.000Z","msg":"依加訓覺 希望聽日精神D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b1a3d06ba1f2fa451e17581b41580745e29069","tid":179802,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"聽asmr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cc8c13632c0584846ad35665560ff99fb3fa97","tid":179802,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽asmr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇好既version推介 以前試過 唔知係咪咁岩都係聽到d麻麻地既